metadata.name: Black Cat in the Green Forest
metadata.description:
May 25 2013, my sister was with a camera around while our cat Neguinho was also around, so I've asked and she took this wonderful photo 📸🖤💚💝

It contains me (still imprisoned in a male body at the time - 2013), my cat Neguinho (lost him in 2014 💔), 2 pokés (parent and child), a monkey, a brazilian jaguar and two hearts 🧙‍♀️🐈‍⬛🐹🐹🐵🐆💞

Originally posted on Facebook, here: https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=368195789948068&id=100002729509262&set=t.100002729509262&eav=AfYuMKK8OIHy1eUJhrWdwFlRK6NIGPKqQdA4aEM1dqWW8qCH32OfvxYjXKnEfo1C6Bk&paipv=0&source=42
